references: Related: CF 175900. Related: Ord 64199, Ord 64712, Ord 65367, Ord 66375, Ord 67405, Ord 71914
summary: An ordinance relating to the concession granted Pacific Coin Lock Company by Ordinances Nos. 64199, 64712, 65367, 66375, 67405 and 71914 for locking certain toilet booths in various public comfort stations in the City; and authorizing a supplemental contract reducing the concession fee.
